{"type": "article", "id": 10439, "title": "几何形曲别针", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-05T07:14:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235635BLRSYGE0F7Uw5xyr.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">荷兰设计工作室 Daphna Laurens 为 Areaware 设计了一系列几何形状曲别针。整个系列采用黑色，红色和绿色，除了普通的三角形和圆形，曲别针还有各种简单但不规则的形状。这一套曲别针是其“二维空间”系列的组成部分，也标志着 Areaware 公司整体策略的转变，即关注广阔的颜色，形状和材料，<a href=\"http://www.daphnalaurens.nl/index.php?/daphna-laurens/daphna-laurens/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看他们更多作品。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235632qJYRXZIEyN3K6OnF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.98288509\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235633Rr8mcTlJAoGYvjkF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.04156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235633zYlXGBUwvOPKt4aI.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.63569682\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235634fq9MAJTmXlL2aSDw.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.39853301\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235634lersRaToO15PI0CA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235634GanoNt7FvzQh46sq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235635VXRmNCvbpsMeZHkD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}